---
// MethodologySection - The Zero Ad Spend Member System: 6 pillar cards
---

<section id="methodology" class="methodology-section">
  <div class="grid-bg"></div>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <span class="section-badge">Our System</span>
      <h2>
        The New Member Pipeline
      </h2>
      <p class="section-desc">
        A complete growth system built for gym and studio owners. We wake up your old leads, bring in friends of your current members, run your ads, and handle every single follow-up so new people keep coming through your doors.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="pillars-grid">
      <div class="pillar-card">
        <div class="pillar-top">
          <div class="pillar-icon-wrap">
            <iconify-icon icon="lucide:zap" class="pillar-icon"></iconify-icon>
          </div>
          <span class="pillar-number">01</span>
        </div>
        <h3>Wake Up Your Old Leads</h3>
        <p>Every gym has hundreds of old leads and past members sitting in the system. We reach out to all of them and pull new appointments from people who already know your gym. Revenue from day one, no ad spend needed.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="pillar-card">
        <div class="pillar-top">
          <div class="pillar-icon-wrap">
            <iconify-icon icon="lucide:users" class="pillar-icon"></iconify-icon>
          </div>
          <span class="pillar-number">02</span>
        </div>
        <h3>Friends of Your Members</h3>
        <p>Your current members are walking billboards. We run a simple referral play that gets their friends, coworkers, and family through your doors. These are the best leads you'll ever get, and they cost you nothing to bring in.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="pillar-card">
        <div class="pillar-top">
          <div class="pillar-icon-wrap">
            <iconify-icon icon="lucide:target" class="pillar-icon"></iconify-icon>
          </div>
          <span class="pillar-number">03</span>
        </div>
        <h3>An Offer People Actually Want</h3>
        <p>We build an offer that makes people stop scrolling and book a consult. Written for your market, your gym, and the kind of members you want walking through the door.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="pillar-card">
        <div class="pillar-top">
          <div class="pillar-icon-wrap">
            <iconify-icon icon="lucide:megaphone" class="pillar-icon"></iconify-icon>
          </div>
          <span class="pillar-number">04</span>
        </div>
        <h3>We Run Your Ads</h3>
        <p>Once your old leads and referrals are producing, we turn on ads to scale. Our team handles everything: writing, design, targeting, testing. You don't touch a thing, and we only run ads that actually bring people through your doors.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="pillar-card">
        <div class="pillar-top">
          <div class="pillar-icon-wrap">
            <iconify-icon icon="lucide:bot" class="pillar-icon"></iconify-icon>
          </div>
          <span class="pillar-number">05</span>
        </div>
        <h3>We Answer Every Lead for You</h3>
        <p>The second someone inquires, we're on it. Texts, calls, follow-ups, all handled for you day and night. No more leads going cold because your front desk is busy running classes. Every person gets a real conversation until they book or say no.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="pillar-card">
        <div class="pillar-top">
          <div class="pillar-icon-wrap">
            <iconify-icon icon="lucide:calendar-check" class="pillar-icon"></iconify-icon>
          </div>
          <span class="pillar-number">06</span>
        </div>
        <h3>Booked on Your Calendar</h3>
        <p>Real people, ready to walk through your doors, show up on your calendar with reminders already sent. You and your team just have to be there, say hi, and sign them up.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .methodology-section {
    position: relative;
    padding: 6rem 0;
    background: var(--surface);
  }

  @media (min-width: 1024px) {
    .methodology-section { padding: 8rem 0; }
  }

  .grid-bg {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background-image:
      linear-gradient(var(--grid-line) 1px, transparent 1px),
      linear-gradient(90deg, var(--grid-line) 1px, transparent 1px);
    background-size: 60px 60px;
    opacity: 0.5;
  }

  .container {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    max-width: 1280px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 1.5rem;
  }

  @media (min-width: 1024px) {
    .container { padding: 0 2rem; }
  }

  .section-header {
    max-width: 48rem;
    margin: 0 auto 4rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .section-badge {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
    background: var(--accent-bg);
    color: var(--accent);
    border-radius: 9999px;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .section-header h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-display, 'Clash Grotesk', sans-serif);
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .section-desc {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .pillars-grid {
    display: grid;
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .pillars-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
  }

  @media (min-width: 1024px) {
    .pillars-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); }
  }

  .pillar-card {
    background: var(--page-bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 1rem;
    padding: 2rem;
    transition: all 0.3s;
  }

  .pillar-card:hover {
    border-color: var(--accent-hover-border);
    transform: translateY(-4px);
  }

  .pillar-top {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    justify-content: space-between;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .pillar-icon-wrap {
    width: 3.5rem; height: 3.5rem;
    background: var(--surface2);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 0.75rem;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    transition: border-color 0.3s;
  }

  .pillar-card:hover .pillar-icon-wrap {
    border-color: var(--accent-hover-border);
  }

  .pillar-icon { color: var(--accent); font-size: 1.5rem; }

  .pillar-number {
    font-family: var(--font-display, 'Clash Grotesk', sans-serif);
    font-size: 2.25rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--number-color);
  }

  .pillar-card h3 {
    font-family: var(--font-display, 'Clash Grotesk', sans-serif);
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .pillar-card p {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
</style>
